                        \ by a factor of 2^X (i.e. divide by 2^X)

 LDA XX12               \ Set XX15 = normal_x
 STA XX15

 LDA XX12+2             \ Set XX15+2 = normal_y
 STA XX15+2

 LDA XX12+4             \ Set A = normal_z

