                        \             + XX15(5 4) * XX12(5 4) / 256

 PHA                    \ Push the result A onto the stack, so the stack now
                        \ contains the dot product XX12 . XX15

 TYA                    \ Set X = Y / 4
 LSR A                  \       = the number of this face * 4 /4
 LSR A                  \       = the number of this face
 TAX

